With the integration of Turkey, the message seems to draw a Europe moving metaphorically on the rails to Asia and the Middle East.
Back at Hydarpasha train station, after another night without sleeping, I rethought these two Germans, Herr Ritter and Herr Conu, who followed the construction of this building 100 years ago.
